Welcome to my channel, I'm Fernando Ulrich, and here you will find analyses and insights on economics, markets, and investments, all presented in Portuguese. 

My journey in the world of finance took a new direction after experiencing the global financial crisis of 2008. This led me to complete a master's degree in Austrian School Economics at URJC in Madrid, focusing on economic cycles and global markets. 

With over two decades of international experience, including stints at renowned groups such as XP Inc, ThyssenKrupp, and Banco Indusval & Partners, I believe that knowledge is the key to anticipating the movements of the world economy and better protecting your assets and investments.
